author: p0tatemoon
body: to be honest, I see it like a workout. I make a daily/weekly plan and I follow through. I can miss a day put I try not to miss 2 days in a row  For example, an easy one would be a morning routine :  Designated 10-15min morning routine to Kendu while having my coffee   * Upvote : Kendu on coingecko, coinmarketcap, certik, lewk, etc... * Check new post/repost on X by main account : like and leave a comment * Check kendu reddit : like all post and comments, leave comments  Then you can add extra stuffs like going on TG, smash all pin post, search for $KENDU on X and smash, print business card/ stickers and leave them around town, shilling in real life, etc...be creative!  I would recommend going super easy, just 5min a day but everyday. Consistency is key and the hardest hurdle  Like working out, I don't really rely on motivation. I just do it. If you need a goal, try to do it for the whole year because that's when we are expecting the crypto bull cycle to run. Afterwards, you can reassess if you want to continue or not

body: No worries! I forgot to also mentionned that any type of work is still work. If you only want to upvote on certik or coinmarketcap that's 100% work  Just like the other member responded, at the end of the day, it is your investment. You can give anything you want : no work at all, 5sec, 5 min, 5 hours, etc  To be honest with you, I was invested in Kendu for a couple of months but did zero work. When I saw the CTO happening and saw how the community got together, I wanted to be part of what makes Kendu so special : "We don't gamble, we work". I started with upvotes here and there. Noticed that I could do a bit more so I put a few minutes more  Just having you write here is great, glad to have you among us!

body: The answer to me is in our output.  During my time in Kendu I have watched countless communities and coins pop up and quickly after fade in to obscurity. I can reflect on our past and achievements and see that what we have done here is truly special.  I am sat comfortably in this position I now hold knowing that I am positioned well for the bull run.  I cant deny that this sideways markets is agitating, but I know that the future is sweet.
